definitions.definition: Not permanent ; existing only for a period or periods of time .
examples: Sally was put in temporary charge of the department while they searched for a full-time replacement.

definitions.definition: Existing only for a short time or short times; transient , ephemeral .

main_definition: Not permanent ; existing only for a period or periods of time .
secondary_definitions: Existing only for a short time or short times; transient , ephemeral .
